                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Alius <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>an<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>orum</abbr></expan> natus <lb n="3"/>XXV mortu<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> est <lb n="4"/>ve&amp;lt;n=V&amp;gt;en&amp;lt;o=E&amp;gt; quia <lb n="5"/>suas iniurias de<lb break="no" n="6"/>fendebat Alias <note>sic</note> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iliae</ex></expan> fecerunt 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 4: Saladino: vevene = &amp;quot;&amp;quot;non bene&amp;quot;&amp;quot;, d.h. unverdientermaßen; Solin: verschrieben aus &amp;quot;&amp;quot;veneno&amp;quot;&amp;quot;. (B): AE 1978: Z. 2/3 und Z. 3/4: Zeilentrenner nicht angegeben. AE 1981: Z. 6/7: Zeilentrenner nicht angegeben.</p>
            </div>
